# .rscignore -- controls what rsconnect::deployApp() actually bundles and
# uploads. Only what's listed here gets EXCLUDED; everything else still ships.
#
# IMPORTANT: this file must sit in the same folder as app.R (the appDir
# you pass to deployApp()), NOT inside McHenry_etal/.

# ---- Raw, full-resolution raster folders ----
# The app only ever reads from McHenry_etal/Processed_for_app/ at runtime
# (see processed_dir in app.R). These raw folders are only needed locally,
# by preprocess_rasters.R, and never by the deployed app itself.
# Leading "/" anchors the path to this folder's root, so these patterns
# match ONLY the raw copies -- not the same-named subfolders that live
# inside Processed_for_app/.
/McHenry_etal/Current_distributions/
/McHenry_etal/Environmental_layers/
/McHenry_etal/Projected_redistribution/
/McHenry_etal/Projected_Kelp_community_change/

# ---- Local-only scripts and files, not needed by the running app ----
App_Deployment.R
preprocess_rasters.R
.RData
.Rhistory

# ---- Windows / GIS tool junk ----
desktop.ini
McHenry_etal/desktop.ini
*.aux.xml
README.txt
